item.title: CVE-2022-4783|2024-08-03T01:48:40.579Z -- unknown -- youtube%20channel%20gallery
item.description: The Youtube Channel Gallery WordPress plugin through 2.4 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
